data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom Home on the 05!! Come and see it yourself. This great property offers a roof that is only 7 years old, newer hardwood floors. The living room offers a beautiful vaulted ceiling, the finished basemant can be used for  an extra bedroom or a nice, beautiful family room. Great fenced in yard, great location. Owners are moving on and they want to pass this beauty to a new owner. We are defitnitely just waiting on you. Ask me or ask your favorite Realtor to show you this Gem!!
